	비밀번호 확인 : <input type="password" name="pass2"><br>
	이름 : <input type="text" name="name"> <br>
	주민번호 : <input type="text" name="jumin1">-<input type="password" name="jumin2"><br>
	성별 : <input type="radio" name="gender" value="1">남
		   <input type="radio" name="gender" value="1">여 <br>
	취미 : <input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="trip">여행
			<input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="book">독서
			<input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="movie">영화감상<br>
